TitMainTitle: Group portrait of wedding party, with one ring bearer, two flower girls, six men, including groom, in center wearing moustache, light colored bow tie, and light colored carnation on left lapel, with seven women, including bride wearing mid length veil, earrings, necklace, light colored wedding dress with scalloped lace collar, long sheer sleeves, and full skirt with sheer overlay, standing on altar of church with clock that reads 7:30, sign on wall that reads "River Jordan", and poster on left that reads "The Future Belongs to Those That Prepare For It! Give! Cheerfully Regularly Liberally & Sacrificially to Building Fund Through The Birthday Rally", possibly in the Sixth Mount Zion Baptist Church
